Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_erb_pack_sym_capt

This register contains either captured control symbol information or the first 4 bytes of captured packet information. The errors that generate partial control symbols can be found in SRIOMAINT()_ERB_ERR_DET. The hardware will not update this register (i.e. this register is locked) while SRIOMAINT()_ERB_ATTR_CAPT[VALID] is set. This register should only be read while this bit is set.
